name: the Garden Gate in RED - Hand Silk Screened Throw Pillow - 10 x 18
description:
'the Garden Gate' was made by recreating my image onto a printing screen and hand printing the image onto fabric. This process gives the textiles a rustic and more vintage look.

The front and back fabric are a prewashed red color with white fabric paint. The pillow is stuffed with premium polyester fiberfill and is 10" x 18".

Please spot clean only.

name: SERIES 1 Print Pack - 12 - 4x6 Print Piece
description:
This is Print Pack Series Number 1. It contains 12 - 4x6 prints all signed and numbered. This is a fun and easy way to display a collage of sketches and photographs creating your own story.

These images are currently either unreleased in my shop or or released in a different size or composition.


*Please note frames are not included with purchase*

Official site discount already applied = $5.00

name: SERIES 5 Print Pack - The Boardwalk - 5 - 4x6 prints
description:
The Boardwalk - Cotton Candy, Roller coasters, summer fun.

This print pack includes 5 - 4" x 6" photographs. Each print is professionally printed on Archival Kodak Glossy paper and has a very small white border.

name: Waiting for the Bus - Alone in the City - 11 x 14 Digital Collage
description:
'Alone in the City' is a digital collage series based on my experiences living alone in London... I hoped to capture the day to day happenings of living in a big city by yourself.

This print is titled 'Waiting for the Bus'. It is printed on an 11" x 14" sheet of archival linen texture Fine Art Paper (the image itself is 9 x 11). It comes signed and titled on the front of the print.

Official site discount already applied = $5.00

name: One Classy Fixture - POSTER SIZE 16 x 20 - CHOOSE YOUR COLOR
description:
The Chandelier - 'One Classy Fixture' - White on Black.

This image is professionally printed on High Quality Kodak Lustre Archival Paper and is 16"x20" in size. It's signed and numbered on the back.

This print ships securely rolled in a tube.
